OL,3,CEx FedEx driver sentenced to death for
OL,4,Cmurder of seven-year-old girl
OL,6,FA former FedEx driver has been
OL,7,Fsentenced to death for the murder of a
OL,8,Fseven-year-old girl after delivering
OL,9,FChristmas gifts to her Texas home.
OL,11,FTanner Horner had pleaded guilty to
OL,12,Fcapital murder just as he was about to
OL,13,Fstand trial for the 2022 killing of
OL,14,FAthena Strand.
OL,16,FAthena's body was found two days after
OL,17,Fshe was reported missing in the rural
OL,18,Ftown of Paradise, near Fort Worth.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
