PN,31202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778087158
OL,3,CEx FedEx driver sentenced to death for
OL,4,Cmurder of seven-year-old girl
OL,6,FHorner had been dropping off a box of
OL,7,FYou Can Be Anything Barbies, a
OL,8,FChristmas present for Athena, her
OL,9,Ffamily said.
OL,11,FA jury dismissed calls from the 34-
OL,12,Fyear-old's lawyers to give him a life
OL,13,Fsentence as he suffered from "various
OL,14,Fmental illnesses" and handed down the
OL,15,Fdeath penalty.
OL,17,FCapital punishment is a legal penalty
OL,18,Fin Texas for capital murder.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
