FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778087158
OL,3,CEx FedEx driver sentenced to death for
OL,4,Cmurder of seven-year-old girl
OL,6,FJurors were shown a video and heard
OL,7,Faudio from inside the van that showed
OL,8,FHorner lifting Athena into the van and
OL,9,Fthen driving away, telling her not to
OL,10,Fscream, or he would hurt her.
OL,12,FHorner then covered the camera, but
OL,13,Fthe audio continued recording.
OL,15,FHorner asks Athena questions,
OL,16,Fincluding how old she was and where
OL,17,Fshe went to school, before stopping
OL,18,Fthe van and telling her they are going
OL,19,Fto "hang out".
