CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778087158
OL,3,CEx FedEx driver sentenced to death for
OL,4,Cmurder of seven-year-old girl
OL,6,FA medical examiner testified that
OL,7,FAthena died of blunt force injuries
OL,8,Fwith smothering and strangulation.
OL,10,FProsecutor James Stainton told jurors
OL,11,Fin opening statements that Horner had
OL,12,Ftold, "lie upon lie upon lie upon lie"
OL,13,Fin the case, including telling
OL,14,Fauthorities that he accidentally
OL,15,Fstruck Athena with his van while
OL,16,Fmaking the delivery and then killed
OL,17,Fher in a fit of panic.
OL,26,@tD@GOUtD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
