PN,31205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778087158
OL,3,CEx FedEx driver sentenced to death for
OL,4,Cmurder of seven-year-old girl
OL,6,FWhile acknowledging during opening
OL,7,Fstatements that the evidence against
OL,8,FHorner was "overwhelming" and
OL,9,F"terrible," Horner's attorney, Steven
OL,10,FGoble, told jurors that Horner's
OL,11,Fmother drank while she was pregnant,
OL,12,Fthat he has autism and suffered from
OL,13,F"various mental illnesses throughout
OL,14,Fhis life" in addition to being exposed
OL,15,Fto a "massive amount of lead."
OL,17,FThe trial was moved from rural Wise
OL,18,FCounty to Fort Worth after Horner's
OL,19,Flawyers argued that he would not have
OL,20,Freceived a fair trial.
